duck: Weno (formerly Moen) is an island municipality of Chuuk State of the Federated States of Micronesia (FSM).

wiki.text:
]] 'Weno' (formerly 'Moen') is an island municipality of Chuuk State of the
Federated States of Micronesia (FSM). It is located in the Chuuk Lagoon and its
urban area in the northwest (villages of Iras, Nepukos, Mwan) serves as the main
center of commerce and is also the state capital. It is the second most populous
island of the FSM with a population of 13,856 at the 2010
Census.<ref>http://www.spc.int/prism/nada/index.php/catalog</ref>
